data.name: UFW_MESSAGE
data.pattern: \[%{DATA}\] \[UFW %{WORD:ufw_action}\] IN=%{DATA:ufw_interface} OUT= (MAC|PHYSIN)=%{DATA:ufw_mac} SRC=%{IP:ufw_src_ip} DST=%{IP:ufw_dest_ip} %{GREEDYDATA:ufw_tcp_opts} PROTO=%{WORD:ufw_protocol} SPT=%{INT:ufw_src_port} DPT=%{INT:ufw_dst_port} %{GREEDYDATA:ufw_tcp_opts}

description.@value: write_utc_timestamp just in case your syslog provides non-utc unmarked timestamped
